<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko" class="h-full">
 <head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com/3.4.17"></script>
  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lucide@0.263.0/dist/umd/lucide.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/_sdk/element_sdk.js"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    * { font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
    html, body, #app { height: 100%; }
    
    @keyframes fade-up { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    @keyframes pulse-strong { 0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); } 50% { transform: scale(1.08); } }
    @keyframes slide-in { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-10px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); } }
    @keyframes spin { from { transform: rotate(0deg); } to { transform: rotate(360deg); } }
    
    .animate-fade-up { animation: fade-up 0.5s ease-out forwards; }
    .animate-pulse-strong { animation: pulse-strong 1s ease-in-out infinite; }
    .animate-slide-in { animation: slide-in 0.3s ease-out; }
    .animate-spin { animation: spin 1s linear infinite; }
    
    ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); border-radius: 3px; }
    ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }
  </style>
  <style>body { box-sizing: border-box; }</style>
  <script src="/_sdk/data_sdk.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
 </head>
 <body class="h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-950 via-slate-900 to-slate-950">
  <div id="app" class="h-full w-full overflow-auto flex flex-col">
   <!-- Header -->
   <header class="sticky top-0 z-20 px-5 py-4 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900/95 to-slate-900/50 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-amber-600/20">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-2">
     <h1 id="appTitle" class="text-2xl font-bold" style="color: #fbbf24;">혈당 관리</h1>
     <div class="flex gap-2">
      <button onclick="toggleHistory()" class="p-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors hover:scale-110" title="측정 기록" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;"> <i data-lucide="history" style="width:18px;height:18px;"></i> </button> <button onclick="toggleStats()" class="p-2.5 rounded-lg transition-colors hover:scale-110" title="📊 통계 및 그래프" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;"> <i data-lucide="bar-chart-2" style="width:18px;height:18px;"></i> </button>
     </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xs" style="color: #cbd5e1;">식전 혈당 입력 → 식사하기 → 2시간 후 식후 측정</p>
   </header><!-- Main View -->
   <div class="sticky top-16 z-10 px-5 py-3 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900/80 to-slate-900/30 backdrop-blur-sm border-b border-amber-600/10 space-y-2">
    <p class="text-xs font-bold" style="color: #f59e0b;">오늘의 건강 습관</p>
    <div class="flex gap-2 overflow-x-auto pb-1"><button onclick="logHabitAction('water')" class="flex-shrink-0 px-3 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold whitespace-nowrap" style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2); color: #60a5fa; border: 1px solid #3b82f6;">💧 물 마시기</button> <button onclick="logHabitAction('walk')" class="flex-shrink-0 px-3 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold whitespace-nowrap" style="background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2); color: #22c55e; border: 1px solid #22c55e;">🚶 산책</button> <button onclick="logHabitAction('stretch')" class="flex-shrink-0 px-3 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold whitespace-nowrap" style="background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.2); color: #a855f7; border: 1px solid #a855f7;">🧘 스트레칭</button> <button onclick="logHabitAction('sleep')" class="flex-shrink-0 px-3 py-2 rounded-full text-xs font-bold whitespace-nowrap" style="background: rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.2); color: #8b5cf6; border: 1px solid #8b5cf6;">😴 충분한 수면</button>
    </div>
    <div id="habitCount" class="text-xs" style="color: #cbd5e1;">
     오늘 실천: 0개
    </div>
   </div>
   <div id="mainView" class="flex-1 overflow-auto px-5 py-6 pb-8"><!-- Welcome Screen -->
    <div id="welcomePhase" class="space-y-4">
     <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 text-center animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1) 0%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05) 100%); border: 2px solid #fbbf24;">
      <div class="text-6xl mb-4 animate-pulse-strong">
       📊
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #fef3c7;">혈당 측정</h2>
      <p class="text-sm mb-6" style="color: #cbd5e1;">식전 혈당을 입력하세요</p>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
       <button onclick="startNFCRead()" class="flex-1 py-4 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-all active:scale-95" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%); color: #fff;"> <i data-lucide="smartphone" style="width:24px;height:24px;"></i> NFC 읽기 </button> <button onclick="showInputPhase()" class="flex-1 py-4 px-6 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg flex items-center justify-center gap-3 transition-all active:scale-95" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fbbf24 0%, #f59e0b 100%); color: #000;"> <i data-lucide="plus-circle" style="width:24px;height:24px;"></i> 수동 입력 </button>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="rounded-2xl p-5" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2);">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-3" style="color: #f59e0b;">📋 측정 순서</p>
      <div class="space-y-2 text-xs" style="color: #cbd5e1;">
       <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span style="color: #fbbf24;">1️⃣</span> <span><strong>식전:</strong> 식사 직전 혈당 측정 입력</span>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span style="color: #fbbf24;">2️⃣</span> <span><strong>식사:</strong> 뭐든 자유롭게 드세요</span>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span style="color: #fbbf24;">3️⃣</span> <span><strong>식후:</strong> 2시간 후 알림 → 혈당 측정</span>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span style="color: #fbbf24;">🎯</span> <span><strong>목표:</strong> 식후 혈당 &lt; 140 mg/dL</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div><!-- Input Phase -->
    <div id="inputPhase" class="hidden space-y-4">
     <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1) 0%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05) 100%); border: 2px solid #fbbf24;">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #fef3c7;">🩸 식전 혈당 입력</h2>
      <div class="mb-6">
       <label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #cbd5e1;">식전 혈당 (mg/dL)</label> <input type="number" id="inputBefore" min="40" max="300" value="95" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-center text-2xl font-bold" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 2px solid #60a5fa; color: #60a5fa;">
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
       <button onclick="cancelInput()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;">취소</button> <button onclick="submitBeforeMeal()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: #60a5fa; color: #fff;">다음 → 식사하기</button>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div><!-- Meal Phase -->
    <div id="mealPhase" class="hidden space-y-4">
     <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1) 0%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05) 100%); border: 2px solid #fbbf24;">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #fef3c7;">🍜 식사 내용 기록</h2>
      <div class="mb-6">
       <p class="text-sm font-bold mb-3" style="color: #cbd5e1;">무엇을 드셨나요? (선택사항)</p><input type="text" id="mealInput" placeholder="예: 흰쌀밥, 계란후라이, 국" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-sm" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2); color: #fef3c7;">
      </div>
      <div class="mb-4 p-3 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #f59e0b; border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);">
       ⏰ 식사 시작: <span id="mealStartDisplay">--:--</span><br>
        📍 2시간 후 알림을 받을 예정입니다
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
       <button onclick="cancelMealPhase()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;">돌아가기</button> <button onclick="confirmMealPhase()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: #fbbf24; color: #000;">식사 시작 ✓</button>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div><!-- After Phase -->
    <div id="afterPhase" class="hidden space-y-4">
     <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1) 0%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.05) 100%); border: 2px solid #fbbf24;">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #fef3c7;">📈 식후 혈당 측정</h2>
      <div class="mb-4 p-3 rounded-lg text-xs font-bold" style="background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1); color: #22c55e; border: 1px solid rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);">
       ✓ 식전 혈당: <span id="afterDisplayBefore">--</span> mg/dL<br>
        경과 시간: <span id="elapsedTime">0분</span>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
       <label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #cbd5e1;">식후 혈당 (mg/dL)</label> <input type="number" id="inputAfter" min="40" max="400" value="145" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-center text-2xl font-bold" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 2px solid #ef4444; color: #ef4444;">
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3">
       <button onclick="cancelAfterPhase()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;">돌아가기</button> <button onclick="submitAfterMeal()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: #fbbf24; color: #000;">분석하기</button>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div><!-- NFC Reading -->
    <div id="nfcReadingPhase" class="hidden space-y-4">
     <div class="rounded-2xl p-8 text-center animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.05) 100%); border: 2px solid #3b82f6;">
      <div class="text-6xl mb-4 animate-spin">
       📱
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2" style="color: #fef3c7;">NFC 태그 읽는 중...</h2>
      <p class="text-sm mb-6" style="color: #cbd5e1;">휴대폰을 NFC 태그에 접근시키세요</p><button onclick="cancelNFCRead()" class="w-full py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;">취소</button>
     </div>
    </div><!-- NFC Confirm -->
    <div id="nfcConfirmPhase" class="hidden space-y-4">
     <div class="rounded-2xl p-6 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 0%, rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.05) 100%); border: 2px solid #3b82f6;">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6" style="color: #fef3c7;">📱 NFC 식전 혈당</h2>
      <div class="mb-6"><label class="block text-sm font-bold mb-2" style="color: #cbd5e1;">🩸 식전 혈당 (mg/dL)</label> <input type="number" id="nfcBefore" min="40" max="300" class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-lg text-center text-2xl font-bold" style="background: rgba(0,0,0,0.3); border: 2px solid #60a5fa; color: #60a5fa;">
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-3"><button onclick="cancelNFCConfirm()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1); color: #60a5fa;">취소</button> <button onclick="confirmNFCData()" class="flex-1 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: #3b82f6; color: #fff;">다음 → 식사하기</button>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div><!-- Result Analysis -->
    <div id="resultPhase" class="hidden space-y-4">
     <div id="riseAlert" class="rounded-2xl p-6 text-center animate-fade-up" style="border: 2px solid #ef4444;">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-6">
       <div class="rounded-xl p-3" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-1" style="color: #cbd5e1;">식전</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black" id="glucoseBefore" style="color: #60a5fa;">--</p>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-center justify-center"><i data-lucide="arrow-right" style="width:24px;height:24px;color:#ef4444;"></i>
       </div>
       <div class="rounded-xl p-3" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);">
        <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-1" style="color: #cbd5e1;">식후</p>
        <p class="text-2xl font-black" id="glucoseAfter" style="color: #ef4444;">--</p>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-6">
       <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-2" style="color: #cbd5e1;">혈당 상승폭</p>
       <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 justify-center">
        <p class="text-5xl font-black" id="glucoseRise" style="color: #ef4444;">--</p>
        <p class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #ef4444;">mg/dL</p>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div id="riskBadge" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 rounded-full font-bold text-sm" style="background: #ef4444; color: #fff;">
       높은 위험
      </div>
     </div>
     <div id="categoryInfo" class="rounded-xl p-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2);">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-2" style="color: #f59e0b;">📊 혈당 관리 기준</p>
      <p id="categoryText" class="text-sm" style="color: #fef3c7;"></p>
     </div>
     <div id="exerciseRecommendation" class="rounded-xl p-5 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 100%); border: 2px solid #3b82f6;">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-3">
       <span style="font-size: 28px;" id="exerciseIcon">🏃</span>
       <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #fbbf24;" id="exerciseType">운동 추천</p>
        <p class="text-xs mb-2" style="color: #cbd5e1;" id="exerciseDuration">--</p>
        <p class="text-xs mb-3" style="color: #e0e7ff;" id="exerciseDetail">--</p>
        <div class="flex gap-2">
         <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded" style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); color: #60a5fa;">⏱ <span id="exerciseTiming">--</span></span> <span class="text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded" style="background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3); color: #60a5fa;">💪 <span id="exerciseIntensity">--</span></span>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div id="dietRecommendation" class="rounded-xl p-5 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 100%); border: 2px solid #fb923c;">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <span style="font-size: 28px;">🥗</span>
       <div class="flex-1">
        <p class="font-bold mb-1" style="color: #fbbf24;" id="dietType">식단 추천</p>
        <p class="text-xs mb-2" style="color: #e0e7ff;" id="dietReduction">30-40% 감소 권장</p>
        <p class="text-xs mb-3" style="color: #cbd5e1;" id="dietDetail">--</p>
        <div id="dietTipsContainer" class="space-y-1 mb-3"></div>
        <div class="pt-2" style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.3);">
         <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-1" style="color: #fbbf24;">⚠️ 피하세요</p>
         <div id="avoidFoodsList" class="text-xs mb-2" style="color: #cbd5e1;"></div>
         <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-1" style="color: #fbbf24;">✅ 권장 음식</p>
         <div id="preferFoodsList" class="text-xs" style="color: #cbd5e1;"></div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div id="insightsBox" class="rounded-xl p-4" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.3);">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-2" style="color: #f59e0b;">💡 분석 결과</p>
      <p id="insightText" class="text-sm" style="color: #fef3c7;">분석 중...</p>
     </div><button onclick="saveRecord()" class="w-full py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: #fbbf24; color: #000;">💾 기록 저장</button> <button onclick="resetMeasure()" class="w-full py-3 rounded-lg font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;">+ 다시 측정</button>
    </div>
   </div><!-- History View -->
   <div id="historyView" class="hidden flex-1 overflow-auto px-5 py-6 pb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4 sticky top-0 z-10 -mx-5 px-5 py-3 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 to-transparent">
     <h2 class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #fef3c7;">📋 측정 기록</h2><button onclick="toggleHistory()" class="px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;">닫기</button>
    </div>
    <div id="historyList" class="space-y-2"></div>
    <p id="emptyHistoryMsg" class="text-center py-12 text-sm" style="color: #cbd5e1;">아직 측정 기록이 없습니다</p>
   </div><!-- Stats View -->
   <div id="statsView" class="hidden flex-1 overflow-auto px-5 py-6 pb-8">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4 sticky top-0 z-10 -mx-5 px-5 py-3 bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-900 to-transparent">
     <h2 class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: #fef3c7;">📊 통계</h2><button onclick="toggleStats()" class="px-3 py-1 rounded-lg text-sm font-bold" style="background: rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.1); color: #fbbf24;">닫기</button>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-3">
     <div class="rounded-xl p-4 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 100%); border: 2px solid #3b82f6;">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-4" style="color: #f59e0b;">📈 혈당 추이 (최근 10개)</p>
      <div style="width: 100%; height: 200px; position: relative; margin-bottom: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
       <canvas id="glucoseChart"></canvas>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center text-xs flex-wrap">
       <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
        <div style="width: 3px; height: 3px; background: #60a5fa; border-radius: 50%;"></div><span style="color: #cbd5e1;">식전</span>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
        <div style="width: 3px; height: 3px; background: #ef4444; border-radius: 50%;"></div><span style="color: #cbd5e1;">식후</span>
       </div>
       <div class="flex items-center gap-1">
        <div style="width: 3px; height: 3px; background: #22c55e; border-radius: 50%;"></div><span style="color: #cbd5e1;">목표선 (140)</span>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
     <div class="rounded-xl p-4 animate-fade-up" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251, 146, 60, 0.15) 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 100%); border: 2px solid #fb923c;">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-4" style="color: #f59e0b;">📊 혈당 상승폭 추이</p>
      <div style="width: 100%; height: 160px; position: relative; margin-bottom: 8px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden;">
       <canvas id="riseChart"></canvas>
      </div>
      <p class="text-xs" style="color: #cbd5e1; text-align: center;">목표: 50mg/dL 이하</p>
     </div>
     <div class="rounded-xl p-4" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.2);">
      <p class="text-xs font-bold mb-3" style="color: #f59e0b;">📈 평균 혈당 상승폭</p>
      <p class="text-3xl font-black" id="avgRise" style="color: #fbbf24;">-- mg/dL</p>
      <p class="text-xs mt-2" style="color: #cbd5e1;" id="riseStatus">--</p>
